Issues.Body:
Hi Team,
      I call a function javascript on component typescript file, but it not working, Please help me resolve this issue

Component
```
import '../../../assets/js/gantt/ganttMaster.js';
export class TaskComponent implements OnInit {

  constructor() {}

  ngOnInit() {
    var r = new GanttMaster();
  }
}
```



Error: 
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19401173/64226053-11fd1f00-cf08-11e9-8a09-245c9b71f3cb.png)


Thank you.

